.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6843852367bb565c70c543082df26121895e0bcf","tid":153501,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"Ching我copy左過cc台"},{"pid":"ce352f7093d9d03f4ff0843db7b5471f4fda1146","tid":153501,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啱啱去完日本睇左井上嘅比賽，真係令我熱血沸騰，令我更加想快啲到三月上台打！<br />\n雖然南非拳王好似仲未傾得成事</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">但我哋已經收到唔少日本拳手嘅邀請，希望可以嚟香港比賽。唔知我嘅對手會係咩人呢</span><br />\nDef Boxing Gym #TheWonderKid #CLashOfChampions2<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發覺佢地起承轉合運用得出神入化，紅字簡單交待挑戰冠軍有阻濟，及後藍字立即轉移視線話好多收到日本拳手嘅邀請，最後會唔會又打件無人識既廢柴刷積分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，挑戰左幾年冠軍，次次差唔多就打就換左件二打六對手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前既post真係好撚中<br />\n今次又用呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在擊敗日本拳王向井寬史取得21連勝後，「神奇小子」曹星如便將下個目標瞄準「怪物」井上尚彌，坦言希望下場比賽能夠挑戰這名世界拳王。不過，曹星如的經理人劉志遠（Jay）卻有另一番見解，傾向年底先安排曹星如與前世界拳王河野公平先打一場，藉此觀察星如和井上尚彌的差距；Jay解釋：「井上與河野的對決中，在第8回合擊倒河野；我希望Rex先打河野，看看能在第幾回合擊敗對手。」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />串到呢</blockquote><br />\n我覺得佢連河野都未必敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5518a153eeb9e8e411131df2ce783161b44077e2","tid":153501,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啱啱去完日本睇左井上嘅比賽，真係令我熱血沸騰，令我更加想快啲到三月上台打！<br />\n雖然南非拳王好似仲未傾得成事</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">但我哋已經收到唔少日本拳手嘅邀請，希望可以嚟香港比賽。唔知我嘅對手會係咩人呢</span><br />\nDef Boxing Gym #TheWonderKid #CLashOfChampions2<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發覺佢地起承轉合運用得出神入化，紅字簡單交待挑戰冠軍有阻濟，及後藍字立即轉移視線話好多收到日本拳手嘅邀請，最後會唔會又打件無人識既廢柴刷積分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，挑戰左幾年冠軍，次次差唔多就打就換左件二打六對手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前既post真係好撚中<br />\n今次又用呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在擊敗日本拳王向井寬史取得21連勝後，「神奇小子」曹星如便將下個目標瞄準「怪物」井上尚彌，坦言希望下場比賽能夠挑戰這名世界拳王。不過，曹星如的經理人劉志遠（Jay）卻有另一番見解，傾向年底先安排曹星如與前世界拳王河野公平先打一場，藉此觀察星如和井上尚彌的差距；Jay解釋：「井上與河野的對決中，在第8回合擊倒河野；我希望Rex先打河野，看看能在第幾回合擊敗對手。」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />串到呢</blockquote><br />\n我覺得佢連河野都未必敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過晒氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4204947fe0f249baadc105569a7f244a637e4f10","tid":153501,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"第10戰條友都20勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無排名"},{"pid":"95a7d4c8c4adc17ac2650